# Conventional Commits

Follow [Conventional Commits](https://www.conventionalcommits.org/) specification.

## Scope Examples

Use lowercase, kebab-case: `playwright`, `page-objects`, `config`, `docs`, `tests`

## Examples

See git history for real examples. Common patterns:

```text
feat: add cable selection page object
feat(playwright): implement random product selection
fix(tests): resolve timeout in basket validation

- Increase timeout for notification popup
- Add explicit wait for basket update
```

